                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8837" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0272</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">964 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">以上率下——三峡国际的ESG实践之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Under the above rate -- the ESG practice of China Three Gorges International Corporation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">张晗，王朝政</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">首都经济贸易大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">三峡国际能源投资集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">能源工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ESG；ESG实践；战略实施；能源行业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ESG; ESG practice; Strategy implementation; Energy industry</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ESG理念在国内外市场受到越来越多的关注，ESG越来越成为落实国家新发展理念，助推实现国家“双碳”目标的有效抓手。三峡国际能源投资集团有限公司（简称“三峡国际”）作为一家广泛参与境外清洁能源开发与投资的国有企业，业务涵盖海外水电、风电和太阳能等清洁能源项目，具有先天的ESG基因。2022年初，三峡国际率先在公司内部通过以上率下的方式，开启了ESG引入、搭建、落地等ESG战略引入与融合工作，在经历了战略规划、架构搭建、议题落实等诸多实践以及理念转变、结构调整等诸多变革之后，最终将ESG理念融入企业战略，深入到组织业务的各个层面。三峡国际结合自身特点和实际情况，通过实践吸收、转化、提升ESG理念，完成了ESG本土特色化创新，为企业带来了社会价值和经济价值的双重提升，助力长期可持续发展。三峡国际在ESG实践过程中的创新举措和发展经验值得各大企业借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The concept of ESG (Environmental, Social, and Governance) has garnered increasing attention in both domestic and international markets, emerging as an effective lever for implementing the country&#39;s new development philosophy and facilitating the achievement of the national &quot;dual carbon&quot; goals. As a state-owned enterprise extensively involved in overseas clean energy development and investment, China Three Gorges International Corporation (hereinafter referred to as &quot;TGIC&quot;) boasts inherent ESG strengths with its business portfolio spanning overseas hydropower, wind power, and solar energy projects. At the beginning of 2022, TGIC took the lead in initiating the introduction, establishment, and implementation of ESG strategies within the company through a top-down approach. After undergoing numerous practices in strategic planning, structural setup, and issue implementation, as well as undergoing significant transformations in mindset shifts and structural adjustments, TGIC has successfully integrated the ESG concept into its corporate strategy, penetrating every aspect of its organizational operations. Drawing upon its unique characteristics and actual conditions, TGIC has completed localized and innovative adaptations of ESG principles through practical absorption, transformation, and enhancement. This has resulted in dual enhancements to both social and economic value for the company, contributing to its long-term sustainable development. The innovative measures and developmental experiences of TGIC in its ESG practices serve as valuable references for other enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业社会责任》、《ESG战略规划与实施》、《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">制度理论与战略反应；波特假说；三重底线；利益相关者理论；可持续发展理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-11</td>
                            </tr>
